### Smart Task - AuthController API Test
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Tokens (copy/paste manually after login/register)
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN
@refreshToken = REPLACE_REFRESH_TOKEN

### 1) Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "phong.test@example.com",
  "password": "12345678",
  "fullName": "Phong Test",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar.png"
}

### 2) Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "phong.test@example.com",
  "password": "12345678"
}

### 3) Refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 4) Logout (revoke refresh token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 5) Get current profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6) Update current profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Phong Updated",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/new-avatar.png"
}

### 7) Change password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "12345678",
  "newPassword": "new123456",
  "confirmNewPassword": "new123456"
}
